---
title: Tropical Fish Tacos with Mango Cabbage Slaw and Chipotle Crema
description: There’s an unexpected but quite delightful surprise hidden in these tacos: slivers of golden, nectar-sweet mango. The fruit is tucked into a crisp and tangy red cabbage slaw, providing a dazzling contrast to the spice-rubbed warmth of the tilapia and chipotle smoke in the sour cream drizzle. And even better, all that goodness comes together in a flash: you can have these tacos on the table in just 20 minutes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5a32a65b30a03b52c12b9d82-11cf6f19.jpg
